OL,3,CFrank Lampard shortlisted for
OL,4,CChampionship manager of the year
OL,6,FCoventry City boss Frank Lampard has
OL,7,Fbeen shortlisted for Championship
OL,8,FManager of the Season.
OL,10,FLampard has taken his side to the top
OL,11,Fof the Championship table - in his
OL,12,Ffirst full season in charge at the
OL,13,Fclub.
OL,15,FIn fact, Coventry are on the verge of
OL,16,Fsealing promotion this Saturday, at
OL,17,Fhome against Sheffield Wednesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
