OL,3,CFrank Lampard shortlisted for
OL,4,CChampionship manager of the year
OL,6,FBut it was a tough landscape when the
OL,7,F47-year-old was hired for the job in
OL,8,FNovember 2024 - Coventry were 17th in
OL,9,Fthe Championship.
OL,11,FUnder Lampard, the club climbed the
OL,12,Ftable, and became league leaders
OL,13,Fwithin months at one point. But
OL,14,Feventually missed out on promotion at
OL,15,Fthe playoffs.
OL,17,FThis season, the club's form has
OL,18,Fimpeccable, losing only 7 times so far
OL,19,Fin the league.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
