OL,3,CFrank Lampard shortlisted for
OL,4,CChampionship manager of the year
OL,6,FLampard is up against Millwall's Alex
OL,7,FNeil, Hull City's Sergej Jakirovic and
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough's Kim Hellberg at the
OL,9,F2026 EFL Awards.
OL,11,FThe winners will be announced live at
OL,12,Fa ceremony on Sunday, 19 April.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Coventry goalkeeper Carl
OL,15,FRushworth - who played a pivotal role
OL,16,Fin the club's promotion push - has
OL,17,Falso been shortlisted for Championship
OL,18,FPlayer of the Season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
